{"tid":468574,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"尋找和田玉的故事 非曬命 有圖","createTime":"2017-11-14T13:17:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T06:27:12.000Z","uid":71877,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"386eea478fcdd3a37b47c7cb71bd7dbd6907fe98","tid":468574,"uid":71877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T13:17:37.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲打，事情是咁的，<br />\n話說我返大陸玩左兩日，途經一間首飾店新開張，入去買咗對耳環，價值＄29人仔，獲得兩次抽奬機會。<br />\n係人都知大陸啲店員好Hea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，求其比我抽左兩張刮刮咭佢就轉身走左，叫我自己刮。<br />\n我刮完第一張謝謝惠顧，諗住刮埋第二張都走架啦。點知刮完第二張，上面竟然寫住一等奬！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我過去問佢有咩奬品，唔知佢係咪聽唔明，佢叫我放低咭就走啦(枱面有一個放滿謝謝惠顧咭嘅兜)<br />\n跟住我用普通話同佢講我中咗一等奬喎，跟住佢即刻搶咗我手上張刮刮咭，仔細咁睇左一陣，之後佢問我你係咪啱啱刮架？<br />\n我心諗:頂，唔係啱啱刮張紙係邊度黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c216856c83475e0641ca2821f18822da4937616d","tid":468574,"uid":115724,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T13:19:35.000Z","msg":"???? 圖"},{"pid":"65c89f31fc5ee80d2ac814cfb95167d4864a7005","tid":468574,"uid":71877,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T13:24:58.000Z","msg":"之後佢就叫晒佢啲經理過嚟檢查張咭，檢查完之後就話你真係好幸運，中咗一等奬。可以用一折嘅價錢購買飾櫃嘅產品。<br />\n其實佢啲產品本身都打緊6.8折。<br />\n但係一折又好似好吸引，之後我老公就睇中左一粒吊墜，期間佢哋又話唔可以買超過$5000嘅產品，又話一定要留電話，要打得通，俾公司去check，之後我就問佢係咪折後嘅＄5000？即係50,000以下都可以買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲大陸人唔知係咪數學比較差，撳咗好耐計數機先知50,000嘅一折等於＄5000。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟住回覆我話係！<br />\n最後因為我哋好趕時間就嗱嗱聲買咗呢個價值＄26,900嘅和田玉吊墜。<br />\n下面附圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/14/212451_6635199e096f899875df802ad720ff37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F212451_6635199e096f899875df802ad720ff37.jpg&h=34108b4f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/14/212453_89626025ecdad6a8907c013acdc83688.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F212453_89626025ecdad6a8907c013acdc83688.jpg&h=cc67844c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8f3a7dbdd291bd02f9c5e5a44ded687edf5bbae","tid":468574,"uid":71877,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T13:27:21.000Z","msg":"我想請教咁多位巴打絲打，<br />\n佢呢啲係咪真貨？<br />\n佢有畀晒證書我<br />\n但係大家都知大陸除咗騙子幾乎冇嘢係真架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想請教下如果係真大概值幾多錢？<br />\n係咪真係和田玉？<br />\n又或者係咪真係玉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7751ea85930e9e8164fd6b3617c265e64c29dd0e","tid":468574,"uid":71877,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T13:29:54.000Z","msg":"呢張係證書嘅圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/14/212844_59b35de7b616ec909805f18560651d75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F212844_59b35de7b616ec909805f18560651d75.jpg&h=c4163e83&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/14/212846_7c45db7d5ee603159bce670a15a37acf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F212846_7c45db7d5ee603159bce670a15a37acf.jpg&h=36e116cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢嗰度唔俾我影相，但係為咗保住老母，我都偷偷地影咗一張<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/14/212950_653f6ade9560bd7dc3357b904689922a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F212950_653f6ade9560bd7dc3357b904689922a.jpg&h=f7f9bdff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b48741d5253b772a735dc3ed92d4575f94f5a84","tid":468574,"uid":7050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T13:32:37.000Z","msg":"咁似騙局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d1203aafae4d01a9ee10117a5e4bc1e99ada8f","tid":468574,"uid":71877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T13:33:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁似騙局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就係想問下我係咪俾人呃左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6629abeedde19262ef29afed0d23eece54549f3a","tid":468574,"uid":25313,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T13:35:40.000Z","msg":"d指甲好嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd9baed9cbf655e402d26569c47502b039c66a3","tid":468574,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T13:37:07.000Z","msg":"又撚"},{"pid":"190c4f95106575f38df0e9cd20b5b83520922930","tid":468574,"uid":71877,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T13:37:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>d指甲好嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁影張冇嘅俾你睇啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/14/213717_2be9169566c7f5b0274739a128a45d98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F213717_2be9169566c7f5b0274739a128a45d98.jpg&h=223e4ea9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/14/213717_4ebc209d11168374f6b6cf5893cd958f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F213717_4ebc209d11168374f6b6cf5893cd958f.jpg&h=042f3c0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"edca24514be30df4df43ec2572fb8de453ffe8c7","tid":468574,"uid":141271,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T13:39:08.000Z","msg":"唔好唔開心啦，可能你粒玉同d金既價值高過佢呢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/14/213859_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F213859_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=84c003dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"122edc138808a408049154629873897cdcd7a6b7","tid":468574,"uid":71877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T13:40:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好唔開心啦，可能你粒玉同d金既價值高過佢呢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/14/213859_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F213859_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=84c003dc&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n謝謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ff978850017ddf34f1510a4310ab429abb33dc3","tid":468574,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T20:08:10.000Z","msg":"個證書係真既<br />\n但粒野真唔真就唔個啦"},{"pid":"3fb64992ecfcf5d76f802468ead0813160a39dc7","tid":468574,"uid":34981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T20:16:18.000Z","msg":"我記得睇過類似嘅post"},{"pid":"c218ada5e4bb5c8b0b2ebd62cf89263286d451a9","tid":468574,"uid":37997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T22:47:37.000Z","msg":"我十年前去大陸交流團已經遇過呢啲騙局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又係珠寶店抽獎話中咗兩折，但間嘢平極折咗都幾千蚊一舊嘢...<br />\n我同啲同學聽完佢鳩噏都即刻走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係會有人買既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95fb8e2a662c9e6dc24adac158d22c361a25f082","tid":468574,"uid":48947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T23:13:53.000Z","msg":"咪衰貪心囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce717975e4d4365ad9d7cbf0ba2fb10dfbec9fc3","tid":468574,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T23:19:08.000Z","msg":"打你老母折"},{"pid":"3a27449510ab631a1f9cdeafc03cea2d0553e884","tid":468574,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T23:28:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好唔開心啦，可能你粒玉同d金既價值高過佢呢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/14/213859_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F213859_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=84c003dc&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n依舊舊玉白淨咁多既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1ae802eb6ce63e3717575fa1feb038f10206350","tid":468574,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T23:28:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打你老母折</blockquote><br />\n應該點講"},{"pid":"29decbf27650210e1241bc86db9597b0893cc873","tid":468574,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T23:29:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打你老母折</blockquote><br />\n應該點講</blockquote><br />\n親 百度一下"},{"pid":"b90922996775f5842d7b6cd8e04e0e724a8e3e60","tid":468574,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T23:33:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>打你老母折</blockquote><br />\n應該點講</blockquote><br />\n親 百度一下</blockquote><br />\n親你老母個閪咩"},{"pid":"b0c11a53efb004dfbb4a4a15020676f720666365","tid":468574,"uid":2638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,